OL,6,FYorkshire Water says it is still
OL,7,Funclear what led to the collapse of a
OL,8,Froad which has been closed for more
OL,9,Fthan a month.
OL,11,FThe A646 Halifax Road, which connects
OL,12,Fthe West Yorkshire towns of Hebden
OL,13,FBridge and Todmorden, has been shut to
OL,14,Ftraffic since 13 December.
OL,16,FMotorists have had to use diversions
OL,17,Fof several miles to get around the
OL,18,Fclosure.
