OL,6,FCllr Sarah Courtney, of Calderdale
OL,7,FCouncil, added: "It's difficult to say
OL,8,Fexactly what's caused this at the
OL,9,Fmoment. It's a live situation. What
OL,10,Fwe're trying to do is get it fixed,
OL,11,Fworking together, to het the road open
OL,12,Fas soon as possible."
OL,14,FThe road was originally due to reopen
OL,15,Fon Christmas Eve, but the date was
OL,16,Fthen delayed until 13 January.
OL,18,FCalderdale Council and Yorkshire Water
OL,19,Fnow say the road will remain closed
OL,20,Funtil at least 27 January.
