OL,6,FThe problem has attracted mockery
OL,7,Fonline, with "The Hole" appearing as a
OL,8,Fvisitor attraction on Google reviews.
OL,10,FOne user said: "Superb hole. How many
OL,11,Fit would take to fill the Albert Hall
OL,12,FI'm not sure about. But judging from
OL,13,Fthe size of it, it wouldn't take many."
OL,15,FAnother wrote: "Well worth a day trip
OL,16,Fout - and best of all it's free!"
OL,18,FBut for businesses on the route, it
OL,19,Fhas caused huge problems.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
