OL,6,FPaul Jackson, of fuel supplier Valley
OL,7,FFuels, said: "I just find it
OL,8,Ffrightening, the power these people
OL,9,Fhave, to decimate local communities
OL,10,Fwith seemingly no comeuppance. I think
OL,11,Fthere should be a full public inquiry
OL,12,Finto what is a debacle."
OL,14,FMr Harrison declined to say if
OL,15,Fresidents and businesses would be
OL,16,Fentitled to compensation.
OL,18,FHe said: "We are working very closely
OL,19,Fwith the council to make sure that
OL,20,Fwe're supporting residents, businesses
OL,21,Fthrough the course of this repair."
